---
layout: "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
title: "About"
---

<!-- About Page v3 - Immersive Fantasy Style -->
<section class="relative min-h-screen text-white bg-black overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="Enchanted Forest" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50 z-0">

  <!-- Glowing Filter Overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-black/70 via-purple-800/50 to-indigo-900/80 z-10 backdrop-blur-sm"></div>

  <!-- Starfield (optional effect layer) -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 starfield z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="relative z-20 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 py-32 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-8 text-yellow-100 drop-shadow-xl animate-fade-in">
      ❖ Welcome to <span class="text-pink-300">Fishnini</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-14 animate-slide-up">
      Where the wind hums forgotten songs and lanterns float on dreams. Here, you are not lost — you are rewritten.
    </p>

    <!-- Magical Card -->
    <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-md rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-10 md:p-14 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-zoom-in">
      <p class="text-white/90 text-lg md:text-xl font-light">
        ✧ In Fishnini, the forest speaks your name in echoes.<br>
        ✧ The moon paints your story across the sky.<br>
        ✧ You didn’t come here to flee. You came to begin again.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Back to Top Button -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <a href="#top" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 via-pink-500 to-yellow-400 text-black font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        ↑ Back to Top
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
@keyframes fade-in {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}
@keyframes slide-up {
  from { transform: translateY(30px); opacity: 0; }
  to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}
@keyframes zoom-in {
  from { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0; }
  to { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
}
.animate-fade-in {
  animation: fade-in 1s ease-out forwards;
}
.animate-slide-up {
  animation: slide-up 1.4s ease-out forwards;
}
.animate-zoom-in {
  animation: zoom-in 1.6s ease-out forwards;
}

.starfield {
  background-image: radial-gradient(white 0.8px, transparent 0.8px);
  background-size: 30px 30px;
  opacity: 0.08;
  animation: twinkle 6s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes twinkle {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.05; }
  50% { opacity: 0.15; }
}

h1, h2, h3 {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
}
p {
  font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
}
</style>

